1. what is a virtual machine 
Answer = a vm is virtual instance of a computer that can perform almost  all of the function as a computer including running application and operating system. virtual machine run on a physical machine and access computing resource from software called a hyperwiser 


2. what is hypervisor
a hypervisor is also known as virtual machine monitor or vmm is software that create a run virtual machine (VM). a hypervisor also a host computer to support multiple guests virtually sharing its resource such as memory and processing 


